{"tid":786913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講好一夜情「不能暈船」　她得不到控對方性侵","createTime":"2018-08-20T09:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T21:03:08.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c764684a64cd4e0ae2e8d32b5d159cf6efa2bddc","tid":786913,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"桃園市吳姓男子（27歲）邀約女大生到他租處住，講好一夜情「不能暈船」，隔天兩人一起用餐，吳男發現講到他喜歡的女生時，對方就吃醋抓狂，2人起爭執，1個月後女生控告他性侵。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，檢察官偵辦，吳男表示，和女方先講好「單純性行為，不能陷入感情，也不能講出去」，對方也答應。<br />\n<br />\n2人完事後共浴、同床共眠，吳男隔天發現對方陷入感情，他認為女生「暈船」，不再連絡，否認性侵。女生承認對吳男有好感，答應一夜情，吳撫摸她、幫她脫衣，但未經她同意就上。<br />\n<br />\n檢方認為，女大生1個月後控告性侵，不像遭性侵後痛恨對方，立即報警或求助，對吳男不起訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.sefutbol.com/sites/default/files/u168/gif_ruben_blanco.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.sefutbol.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fu168%2Fgif_ruben_blanco.gif&h=199759a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9beb4cf433f5fd44486da6a056105ad63952d5d","tid":786913,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"5cd61c1ead1e40bf0c9ebb139bf0af578bd8d2fa","tid":786913,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f63b1f65a499db21d1f162d813a51f2a4d2e738","tid":786913,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"#越想越不對勁"},{"pid":"a11f5cac445d92b8ef6b0c97015b7bafe7c99deb","tid":786913,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"扑野同意書"},{"pid":"5bc3486b09790b990ce434fc0fb9eb60da11fcd1","tid":786913,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T20:55:28.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"3635f58a13b641389660d1695489fc0120d1c3af","tid":786913,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T21:03:08.000Z","msg":"所以話 台灣應該制定一張做愛同意書 公佈於政府網站 公共場所 便利店<br />\n等民眾方便領取 下載 隨時隨地都拎到<br />\n減少商業糾紛及私人糾紛 以免浪費警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}